data.description: Wow! This house has 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. It is sparkling clean with fresh paint throughout. It offers easy access to 45 South, Beltway 8, and Highway 3. The spacious covered patio is great for entertaining family and friends. If you need space for your tools, there is a  shed 10x 9  available for all your yard equipment to keep your backyard tidy.
